text:
@faz3 thou art my dearest 💜;
I miss thee day and night;
I keep wishing to the stars above;
for my hope and dream to come true;
love, love and love you; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 be it sunshine;
be it rain;
it’d be fine;
as long as one sees thee again and again;
the night be serene;
the time be late;
lethargy wouldn’t stop me;
for this 💜 be forever; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 missing thee tonight o my dearest Prince;
I beseech thee forget one not;
for one adores thee and long for thy presence;
stay true, stay safe;
most of all, stay mine;💜🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 oh my dearest Prince of tranquility;
wherever thou art;
this 💜 be always missing thee; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 my 💜 be such that river can’t quench;
with thy presence does it persevere;
and nor ought but thy face and smile be its recompence; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 this forlorn 💜 be
ever looking at thee;
thou who art far away
from one;
this loving rendition that calls to mind thy soulful face;
the joy of feeling and oh the dream of meeting;
how I wish to adore thee; to love thee even more; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 if one notes thy presence again;
let it be that the calamity be over;
my dearest Prince;
whose face inhabits my 💜 forever;
thy soulful eyes in my soul;
and one misses thee terribly; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 thou art in one’s 💜 no matter what;
despite spending the day in toil;
thou art in my very thought;
as one burns the midnight oil; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 where art thou my dearest Prince I’ve got to ask;
thinking of thee at all times;
missing thy face even more;
this 💜 be ever thine; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 oh all one has are these words;
for thee to remember me my dearest Prince;
as thou art in one’s thoughts;
ever so constantly;
thou increases this longing;
this 💜 only wishes to adore thee; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 missing thee, thyself and thy presence;
the face of my beloved;
who makes this toil and strife worthwhile;
with thee love ain’t merely a forlorn word;
more than a smile; thou art everything good and kind; 💜🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 oh the 🌳;
the sign of this 💜 may thou find;
in thy heart to remember one;
who thinks of thee
with adoration and utmost regard;
may the long distance 
only makes the sentiment grow fonder;
between thou and one; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥☕️📷💙

@faz3 one keeps saying thou art awesomeness;
that thou art my one and only;
these lines be for my dearest Prince;
word for word;
thou art masterful in shi’r (poetry); pray thou would be in cognizant with these lines;💜🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 especially to my dearest Prince;
this night time serenade seeks to find;
thee in the best of temperament to consider my words;
came straight from my 💜 for thee and only thee; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 my Prince, my 💜;
oh where art thou;
as for ever thou art my beloved;
one’d always crave 
for thy presence; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 sir “I asked my country  rulers for a Little help,
but they all my rulers  ignored my request.
Now I want to ask you for a little help please sir.”🇵🇰🙏

@faz3 thinking of my dearest Prince in the night;
where silence permeates and tranquility rules;
thou art my beloved no matter what;
thy face be the one
that soothes and cures; 💜🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 hope it’d be raining in thy golden sand country;
as hither the drizzle continues almost effortlessly;
my forlorn 💜 is salvaged by thy presence;
wishing thou art here my dearest Prince; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 miss you and love you my dearest Prince;
wherever thou art;
this 💜 be thine for always; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 blessed be this day for its swell weather;
and furry friends with their sustenance (though to date the white one’s gone gallivanting);
later in the day perchance it shall emerge;
these be the mundane things that keep me going;
this utmost 💜 for my dearest Prince or else there wouldn’t be anything happening; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 where be my dearest Prince, beloved to one’s💜;
this yearning for thee will go on and on;
for always and for ever; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 💜 greetings to my dearest Prince;
on a partially sunny afternoon;
afresh after a light drizzle; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

Hello. Do you know any wealthy, kind people who do charity work? Our shelter desperately needs financial help to buy food for the dogs. Please help us find sponsors. +375296617510 WhatsApp
  PayPal
  @Hatiko78

@faz3 I implore forgiveness if I wrongly pride;
and put on this lonesomeness akin to a badge;
pray do not set one up with disgrace;
when all one does be worship thy face;
for one’s already more rich in hope;
with thee no thoughts I’d find despising;
nor look upon myself and curse my fate;
from time to time I’d pen down me own scope;
so poignant be this sweet love thy richly state brings;
till I scorn to change my state with (anything); 💜🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@zaidkhalefah @faz3 
Do you forget me? 
I was thinking of you will be my فزعة to achieve my dream .
